articles.title: Australia expels Iranian diplomats, accuses country of directing antisemitic arson attacks - CBS News
articles.description: Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese says Iran directed two antisemitic attacks in the country, and diplomatic relations will now end.
articles.content: Melbourne, Australia — Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese accused Iran of organizing two antisemitic attacks in Australia and said the country was cutting off diplomatic relations with Tehran… [+6950 chars]
